en-US.title: Washington Regional Medical Center
en-US.description: Washington Regional Medical Center provides comprehensive healthcare services with a focus on quality and compassion. They integrate competent medical practice with culturally responsive care for the transgender community. Their staff includes experienced, skilled, and compassionate doctors, in a full range of medical specialties. In addition, they provide interpreters at no charge assisting in providing more comfortable healthcare service for people of different lingual backgrounds.

address: 146 Passion Play Rd #A, Eureka Springs, AR 72632, USA
